    <td class="postcell">
        <div>          
            <div class="post-text">
                <p>Do you know any <strong>hidden</strong> or <strong>little-known</strong> nice <strong>feature</strong> of Mac OS X? It doesn't matter what it is&mdash;maybe just a short terminal command. Share your experiences on hidden OS X features here.</p>

<p>Please post <strong>one tip</strong> per answer. Also provide details on how to achieve that feature, and if possible, include a relevant image too!</p>

            </div>            
