            <div class="post-text"><p>While Cmd tabbing between applications, without releasing CMD, you can hit 'Q' to quit or 'H' to hide the selected application. Works great with the mouse to get rid of a whole bunch of applications quickly.</p>

<p>The bevel won't go away and you can repeat this for as many applications as you like as long as you're holding CMD.</p>
</div>
