            <div class="post-text"><p>In most Mac apps (TextEdit, for example), you can <kbd>option</kbd>-drag* to select a rectangular area of non-contiguous text.</p>

<p>*Hold <kbd>option</kbd> while dragging your mouse over an area</p>
</div>
