            <div class="post-text"><p>When I first switched to Mac a couple of years back, I was using it full time for nearly six months before someone showed me <kbd>cmd</kbd>+<kbd>Space</kbd> to bring up the Spotlight Search. Single best shortcut I've learned.</p>
