        <td class="comment-text"><div><span class="comment-copy">Addendum to this: the Spotlight search field can handle simple mathematical expressions. No need for Calculator.app for a quick bit of division!</span> &ndash;&nbsp;<a href="/users/43/lesspop-morefizz" title="439 reputation" class="comment-user">LessPop_MoreFizz</a> <span class="comment-date"><span title="2010-08-24 14:53:35Z">Aug 24 at 14:53</span></span></div></td>
