        <td>
            <div class="post-text"><p>When you drag and drop any file (or folder) from <strong>Finder</strong> onto a <strong>Terminal</strong> window, it gets converted into the full (absolute) path to that file.</p>

<p>I find this a small but occasionally useful trick when dealing with files in both Finder and Terminal.</p>
</div>
