        </td>
        <td>
            <div class="post-text"><p>This is a pretty common one, but to show all hidden files you can type the command</p>

<pre><code>defaults write com.apple.Finder AppleShowAllFiles 1
</code></pre>

<p>and then</p>

<pre><code>killall Finder
</code></pre>

<p>in Terminal.</p>

<p>To reverse, repeat using a 0 instead of 1.</p>
</div>
            <table class="fw">
            <tr>
            <td class="vt">
                <div class="post-menu"><a href="/questions/400/mac-os-x-hidden-features-and-nice-tips-tricks/466#466" title="permalink to this answer">link</a><span class="lsep">|</span><a id="flag-post-466" title="flag this post for serious problems or moderator attention">flag</a></div>
                
