        </td>
        <td>
            <div class="post-text"><p><strong>Drag and drop files and folders to "Open" dialogs/sheets</strong>: very useful to open package contents with other software.</p>

<p>Just locate the file with the Finder</p>

<p><img src="http://i.imgur.com/cXQTh.png" alt="chess.icns"></p>

<p>and drag and drop it to the Open dialog</p>

<p><img src="http://i.imgur.com/cK0BZ.png" alt="open dialog"></p>

<p><strong>Bonus: you can do the same thing with 'Upload file' web forms.</strong> (Only with WebKit-based browser)</p>

<p><img src="http://i.imgur.com/S5TD4.png" alt="drop in browser"> ➔ <img src="http://i.imgur.com/J5ngU.png" alt="dropped"></p>
</div>
