        </td>
        <td>
            <div class="post-text"><p>Running </p>

<pre><code>pmset noidle
</code></pre>

<p>in Terminal will prevent your Mac from sleeping. Press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>C</kbd> to stop.</p>
</div>
            <table class="fw">
            <tr>
            <td class="vt">
                <div class="post-menu"><a href="/questions/400/mac-os-x-hidden-features-and-nice-tips-tricks/1459#1459" title="permalink to this answer">link</a><span class="lsep">|</span><a id="flag-post-1459" title="flag this post for serious problems or moderator attention">flag</a></div>
                
