        </td>
        <td>
            <div class="post-text"><p>Want tab to go to every field on a form not just input fields?</p>

<p>I got sick of the state/country drop down fields of web forms being skipped when tabbing.</p>

<p>Go to <strong>System Preferences</strong> => <strong>Keyboard</strong> and set <strong>Full Keyboard Access</strong> to <strong>All Controls</strong></p>

<p><img src="http://i.imgur.com/4qLZj.jpg" alt="alt text"></p>
</div>
            <table class="fw">
