        <td>
            <div class="post-text"><p>Most applications on OS X respect bash shortcuts for maneuvering about in text fields.</p>

<ul>
<li><p><kbd>CTRL</kbd>+<kbd>A</kbd>: beginning of line.</p></li>
<li><p><kbd>CTRL</kbd>+<kbd>E</kbd>: end of line.</p></li>
<li><p><kbd>CTRL</kbd>+<kbd>U</kbd>: delete from cursor to beginning of line.</p></li>
<li><p><kbd>CTRL</kbd>+<kbd>K</kbd>: delete from cursor to end of line.</p></li>
</ul>

<p>There are others that are slipping my mind currently I'm sure. I miss this so much on Linux.</p>
</div>
