        <td>
            <div class="post-text"><p><strong>Show the full directory path in the Finder window.</strong> </p>

<p>In the Terminal, run this:</p>

<pre><code>defaults write com.apple.finder _FXShowPosixPathInTitle -bool YES
</code></pre>

<p>Then, run this.</p>

<pre><code>killall Finder
</code></pre>

<p>There are all sorts of hidden defaults that can be mucked around with but this is my absolute favorite because now no matter which window I am looking at, I know <em>exactly</em> where I am.</p>
</div>
