    <a name="1617"></a>
    
    <div id="answer-1617" class="answer">
        
        <table>
        <tr>
        <td class="votecell">
            
<div class="vote">
    <input type="hidden" value="1617">
    <a class="vote-up-off" title="This answer is useful (click again to undo)">up vote</a>
    <span class="vote-count-post">5</span>
    <a class="vote-down-off" title="This answer is not useful (click again to undo)">down vote</a>

</div>

        </td>
        <td>
            <div class="post-text"><ul>
<li><p>When typing text in any document or text field <code>alt</code>+<code>backspace</code> will delete the entire word, the same with <code>alt</code>+<code>del</code> which will delete the whole next word.</p></li>
<li><p>Using an accented language? Press <code>ctrl</code>+<code>shift</code>+<code>backspace</code> after an accented letter to delete just the accent, not the letter.</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
            <table class="fw">
            <tr>
            <td class="vt">
                <div class="post-menu"><a href="/questions/400/mac-os-x-hidden-features-and-nice-tips-tricks/1617#1617" title="permalink to this answer">link</a><span class="lsep">|</span><a id="flag-post-1617" title="flag this post for serious problems or moderator attention">flag</a></div>
                
            </td>
            
            <td align="right" class="post-signature">
