            </td>
            
            <td align="right" class="post-signature">
            <div class="user-info"><div class="user-details"><span class="community-wiki" title="This post is community owned as of Sep 15 at 20:06. Votes do not generate reputation, and it can be edited by users with 100 rep">community wiki</span></div><br><div class="user-details"><a id="history-1617" href="/posts/1617/revisions" title="show revision history for this post">gregseth</a></div></div>
